text: Shahrak-e Sarab Nilufar is a village in the Baladarband Rural District in the Central District of Kermansah County, Kermanshah province, Iran. According to the 2006 Iranian census, the population of the village was 1,018 people with 249 families. == References == Category:Villages in Iran Category:Pages with unreviewed translations Category:Kermanshah Province
